9752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係呢一part 宏利北美係收緊0.74%，永明行業股票收緊0.3%，HSBC自選美股 係收緊0.05%，你老味萬全美股係0呀<br />\n<br />\n係收費上絕對反映到agent係各街頭網絡推銷既積極程度，羊毛出在羊身上嘛"},{"pid":"336fef00aa4cf730e46ccfe86d55374886631b7b","tid":2495567,"uid":29744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c7f6c93bdce3130dc300b7f283e915d8c72b24c","tid":2495567,"uid":65643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e68a499e6551e3516b04880745d5ff7cd2337da","tid":2495567,"uid":29744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4721334ef413959c3fd127bf834a11f49cdf69fa","tid":2495567,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:51:34.000Z","msg":"半自由行係一年度做一次，我通常每年11月就會預約個時間<br />\n將公司個人供款部份轉走<br />\n不過各間公司個行政效率真係低撚到要3星期左右先完成交接買賣<br />\n其實HSBC 自選美股已經係投資非港股大支那市場外最平既一個基金<br />\n<br />\n不過都係果句，DIS 是一個好東西來，懶人唔想轉就用佢啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:58:30.000Z","msg":"話說你點睇積金易平台，政府諗住自己攬晒D行政工作去呢個平台，以後所有行政工作 (加減成員、轉基金、僱主供款 etc) 都要用呢個平台搞<br />\n<br />\n希望呢次行政中央化真係可以搞高效率啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:07:12.000Z","msg":"佢d報告好垃圾<br />\n回報表現最短都係睇一年<br />\n想睇3個月表現都無"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T03:35:00.000Z","msg":"我唔係講緊強積金比較平台，係另一舊野黎&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfa.org.hk/empf/overview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfa.org.hk%2Fempf%2Foverview&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx6Ggm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=ce389a80\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfa.org.hk/empf/overview</a>"},{"pid":"188d721700dd1831d8833a27eec482446f07c023","tid":2495567,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T04:10:26.000Z","msg":"原來富達咗廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47ab0942d67d2d880adb9e115c0a8fdd3a6d683","tid":2495567,"uid":46407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:04:28.000Z","msg":"個mpf profile 好似2年無郁過<br />\n<br />\n用緊永明，40%港股，40%行業，20%恒指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces